divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving south on I-169 from about 5 miles north of Milaca when I noticed an odd bright white light in the sky probably somewhere over princeton off in the distance. It was up at an altitude that it could have been a jet however there was no jet stream and it is in the single digits degrees farenheit. It then appeared to turn and the light was no longer shining in my direction but I could see a craft of some sorts it was at a distance that the shape was undistinguishable, then all of a sudden I could no longer see it as if it just zoomed off, however there was no sign of a jet stream and it disappeard very suddenly. Five minutes later I see a jet heading in the direction the craft appeard to take off in and another five minutes later another jet heading in the same direction.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Princeton
This sighting has never been favorited.
Summary: Bright light hovering that appeared to turn and disappear.
